    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_9_2219-2327",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2219-2327",
      "markText": "是白垩纪晚期地球的大陆形状和分布，其中最大的那一块就是冈瓦纳古陆。” “白垩纪？距现在有多长时间？！” ",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2219&rangeEnd=2327",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2219&rangeEnd=2327"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_12_811-821",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "811-821",
      "markText": "丁仪教授走进了大厅。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=811&rangeEnd=821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=811&rangeEnd=821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_11_13652-13680",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "13652-13680",
      "markText": "同时，我自己也不喜欢小说中很重的殖民主义和霸权主义色彩。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=13652&rangeEnd=13680",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=13652&rangeEnd=13680"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_3_34905-34928",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "34905-34928",
      "markText": "那有什么不好？在这艰难时代，懂的少些就舒服些。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=34905&rangeEnd=34928",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=34905&rangeEnd=34928"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_5_32095-32168",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "32095-32168",
      "markText": "我们不必留恋所谓过去的好时光，那个时候生活充满艰难危险和迷惘；我们也不必为今天的时代过分沮丧，因为今天，也总有一天会被人们称做是——过去的好时光。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=32095&rangeEnd=32168",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=32095&rangeEnd=32168"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_4_14806-14871",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14806-14871",
      "markText": "当生存问题完全解决，当爱情因个体的异化和融和而消失，当艺术因过分的精致和晦涩而最终死亡，对宇宙终极美的追求便成为文明存在的唯一寄托",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14806&rangeEnd=14871",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14806&rangeEnd=14871"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_7_3773-3798",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3773-3798",
      "markText": "暴雨连下几十年，大地被进一步冷却，海洋渐渐恢复了。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3773&rangeEnd=3798",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3773&rangeEnd=3798"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_13_4459-4494",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4459-4494",
      "markText": "据现代物理学和生物学的推测，我们人类在宇宙中出现的几率可只有几亿分之一",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4459&rangeEnd=4494",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4459&rangeEnd=4494"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_3_5225-5273",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5225-5273",
      "markText": "如果精细的小部件造不出来，那些恐龙能够生产的大部件也无法装配成能够使用的成品，所以也都停止生产了",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5225&rangeEnd=5273",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5225&rangeEnd=5273"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_3_8132-8158",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8132-8158",
      "markText": "我们永远也不可能拥有恐龙的两样东西：好奇心和想像力。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8132&rangeEnd=8158",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8132&rangeEnd=8158"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_8_2593-2647",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2593-2647",
      "markText": "我不明白，这样多的钱和物，这样多的人力，能灌溉多少沙漠，使那里长满萄葡和哈密瓜，可你们干的事情，谁都不明白。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2593&rangeEnd=2647",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2593&rangeEnd=2647"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_14_20857-20907",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "20857-20907",
      "markText": "但科幻小说的魅力之一是：它可以对自然规律进行一些改变，然后展示在这种改变之后宇宙是如何带着硬伤运行的",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=20857&rangeEnd=20907",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=20857&rangeEnd=20907"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_9_3892-3925",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3892-3925",
      "markText": "这过程极其短暂，像是太空眨了一下眼，难怪上次穿过时我们没有觉察到。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3892&rangeEnd=3925",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3892&rangeEnd=3925"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_11_1692-1758",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1692-1758",
      "markText": "中国国旗降下后，英国国旗在《上帝保佑女王》的乐声中升起，在旗的上缘接触杆顶时，时钟刚刚走过零点，这时，我们在这块土地上已是外国人了。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1692&rangeEnd=1758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1692&rangeEnd=1758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_3_7357-7398",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7357-7398",
      "markText": "皇帝点点头，“要与它们同时行动，以防让多多米做好人，把蚂蚁联邦拉到罗拉西亚那边去。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7357&rangeEnd=7398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7357&rangeEnd=7398"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_11_4967-4982",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "4967-4982",
      "markText": "就象欧洲人仍把中国人叫洋人一样",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4967&rangeEnd=4982",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4967&rangeEnd=4982"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_6_9715-9782",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9715-9782",
      "markText": "第二天人们发现他冻死在那里，一只手伸进怀中，握着他用鲜血换来的勋章，睁大双眼看着这个他在七十多年前从古德里安的坦克群下拯救的城市……”",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9715&rangeEnd=9782",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9715&rangeEnd=9782"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300096146_12_6954-6982",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "6954-6982",
      "markText": "这就是统一场数学模型的计算结果中那个负时间参量的含义？！",
      "totalCount": 26,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300096146&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6954&rangeEnd=6982",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8db32080813ab8c0eg01682a?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6954&rangeEnd=6982"
    },
    {
